    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You and your allies are poised to pounce whenever one of you scores a telling blow.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Combat Reflexes, Improved Critical.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When an ally who also has this feat confirms a critical hit against an opponent that you also threaten, you can make an attack of opportunity against that opponent.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When an ally with this feat threatens a critical hit but fails to confirm it, you can spend 5 stamina points to make your attack of opportunity anyway.",
